race.comment: WRITTEN FAME (6) sharp winner two back over this track and trip. Sent straight to town when raced without luck from the wide gate to finish eighth over 1200m at Doomben. Winning rider hops back on and brings a superior set of figures here. PANTELONE (2) gripped on late two-back, before sitting on the pace with the claim when a tough winner over 1200m at Rockhampton. Will give a sight again. SARSEN (8) on the backup when a long overdue winner in average company over 1540m at the Gold Coast Poly. Hard fit and gets map favours. BEAN FOGGY (3) is resuming from a break. Fitter for a recent trial at Ballina and in the mix.
